Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP「LOVE or HATE?」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:24.62,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}たとえば髪をちょっとなびかせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:27.87,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}聴こえる声{\fsp4}は{\fsp0}LOVE or HATE？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:31.93,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お好きにどうぞ　何と言われても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.88,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}足は止めませんから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:38.38,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}飛ぶ鳥落とす勢い　ニュース
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:41.37,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}明日には忘れている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:45.35,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}昨日よりも今日がいいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:48.30,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}思い込み　大勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:51.85,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}リズムに合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:55.31,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}揺れていたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:58.85,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}外野がうるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:02.14,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ノイズ・キャンセリング
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.62,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}たとえば指をちょっとなぞらせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:08.77,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君のチョイス{\fsp4}は{\fsp0}LOVE or HATE？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:12.87,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お好きにどうぞ　頬を赤くして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.85,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}唾を吐きかけ{\fsp4}る{\fsp0}Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:19.45,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}趣味の違い　安心の相違が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君を戸惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:25.72,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}私の道　形作るのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:29.49,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}これだけ　Just LOVE or HATE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:24.62,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是撩一下头发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:27.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}听到的会是喜欢还是讨厌？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:31.93,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}随便吧 无论别人怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.88,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}反正不会停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:38.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}新闻的传播势不可挡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:41.37,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}到了明天就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:45.35,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}所以今天比昨天好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:48.30,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}精神胜利大法好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:51.85,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}本想跟着节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:55.31,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}摇摆摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:58.85,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但外面也太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:02.14,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}噪音·消除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.62,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是用手指转个圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:08.77,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你的选择是喜欢还是讨厌？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:12.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}随便吧 憋红了脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.85,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}准备唾弃的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:19.45,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}兴趣的不同 信仰的不一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.61,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}让你感到迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:25.72,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但决定我前行方向的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:29.49,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}仅仅是喜欢还是讨厌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,IN「Ray of Light」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:59.37,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}青く澄んだ　空は昨日と同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:04.59,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}はずなのに　少し不安で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:11.04,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}いつものように　笑えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:17.30,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あの花のように　咲けるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:22.43,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}うつむきそうな今日を　照らしてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:31.74,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}出逢い　運命が動き出したの　微笑みの魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:38.88,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}愛で満ちてく　勇気と共{\fsp4}に{\fsp0}My heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:43.78,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あなたがくれた　この奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:52.22,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}前を向けたよ　きらめきはどこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:57.84,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}のびてゆく光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:13.51,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}強く吹いた　風は明日に向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:18.87,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}置いてかれてしまいそうな　気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:24.31,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}涙で濡れた頬を　拭ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:34.54,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}触れた　指先が熱く残るの　ときめきの魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:53.09,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}いつものように　笑えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:59.65,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あの花のように　咲ける{\fsp4}よ{\fsp0}My Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:07.70,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}愛で満ちてく　勇気と共{\fsp4}に{\fsp0}My heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:12.72,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あなたがそばに　いるからね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:20.93,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}前に進むよ　きらめきはどこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:27.68,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}のびてゆけ光
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.47,0:18:59.37,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}清澈的天空 如同往日一样
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.37,0:19:04.59,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}却感到了些许不安
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.57,0:19:11.04,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果一如既往地欢笑
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.04,0:19:17.30,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}能够像那朵花一样绽放吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.30,0:19:22.43,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}悲观的时光 得以照亮
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.43,0:19:31.74,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}相遇转动了命运的齿轮 微笑的魔法
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.74,0:19:38.88,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}爱和勇气充满了我的心
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.88,0:19:43.78,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你给予我的这份奇迹
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.78,0:19:52.22,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}让我能够昂首向前 光辉无限扩张
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.22,0:19:57.84,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不断前进的光芒
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.42,0:20:13.51,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}风儿向着明天猛烈地吹着
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.51,0:20:18.87,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}感觉自己要被抛在原地
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.87,0:20:24.31,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你抹去了我脸上的泪水
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.31,0:20:34.54,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}指尖的热量留在了心间 心动的魔法
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.51,0:20:53.09,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果一如既往地欢笑
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.09,0:20:59.65,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就能够像那朵花一样绽放 我的梦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.78,0:21:07.70,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}爱和勇气充满了我的心
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.70,0:21:12.72,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}因为你陪伴在我身边
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.72,0:21:20.93,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我会昂首向前的 光辉无限扩张
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.93,0:21:27.68,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}前进吧 光芒
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「LOVE or HATE?」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:25.01,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}たとえば髪をちょっとなびかせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:28.41,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}聴こえる声{\fsp4}は{\fsp0}LOVE or HATE？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:31.99,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お好きにどうぞ　何と言われても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:35.79,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}足は止めませんから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:39.06,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}飛ぶ鳥落とす勢い　ニュース
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:41.93,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}明日には忘れている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:45.71,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}昨日よりも今日がいいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.49,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}思い込み　大勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:52.56,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}リズムに合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:55.95,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}揺れていたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.45,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}外野がうるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:02.31,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ノイズ・キャンセリング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:06.26,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}たとえば指をちょっとなぞらせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:09.68,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君のチョイス{\fsp4}は{\fsp0}LOVE or HATE？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:13.12,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お好きにどうぞ　頬を赤くして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.31,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}唾を吐きかけ{\fsp4}る{\fsp0}Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:20.02,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}趣味の違い　安心の相違が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:22.90,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君を戸惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:26.42,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}私の道　形作るのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.92,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}これだけ　Just LOVE or HATE
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.66,0:22:25.01,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是撩一下头发
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.01,0:22:28.41,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}听到的会是喜欢还是讨厌？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.41,0:22:31.99,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}随便吧 无论别人怎么说
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.99,0:22:35.79,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}反正不会停下脚步
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.79,0:22:39.06,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}新闻的传播势不可挡
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.06,0:22:41.93,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}到了明天就忘了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.62,0:22:45.71,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}所以今天比昨天好
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.49,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}精神胜利大法好
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.07,0:22:52.56,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}本想跟着节奏
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.56,0:22:55.95,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}摇摆摇摆
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.45,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但外面也太吵了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.45,0:23:02.31,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}噪音·消除
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.85,0:23:06.26,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是用手指转个圈圈
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.26,0:23:09.68,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你的选择是喜欢还是讨厌？
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.68,0:23:13.12,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}随便吧 憋红了脸
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.31,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}准备唾弃的男孩
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.31,0:23:20.02,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}兴趣的不同 信仰的不一
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.02,0:23:22.90,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}让你感到迷茫
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.90,0:23:26.42,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但决定我前行方向的
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.92,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}仅仅是喜欢还是讨厌
